English:

This a test demo for face keyboard.

It's include customing the keyboard toolbar

create a face keyboard view, and click a button on the keyboard toolbar to popup the face-keyboard

if press the face there would be a code-string stand for the face in the text-view.

Then click the change button on the top-right, the text view will show the text with the face image rather than the code-string

Weakness:

1. face keyboard view add too much buttons, the performance not good

   should use UITouch to improve

2. The richTextView should use Core Text to improve the performance.



中文：

（尼玛，写英文真费劲啊！）

这是一个表情键盘的demo，

包括键盘上自定义的工具条

创建一个表情键盘View 点击工具栏的按钮可以弹出这个表情键盘

点击表情会在Text-View中显示该表情对应的编码

点击右上角的转换按钮就可以将编码转换成表情显示出来

